$=\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n^{2}}\left[\sum_{k=1}^{n} k \ln \left(1+\frac{k^{2}}{n^{2}}\right)+\sum_{k=1}^{n} k \ln n^{2}+\ln n^{-n(n+1)}\right]$
